                                                                                                                           17                                                                                      Dhaka clashes
                            
	Dhaka, June 30 (Reuters): More than 80 Bangladeshis were wounded today in clashes with police sparked by the arrest of three politicians charged with offences ranging from murder to insulting Islam and demands by textile workers for a pay rise.                                                                                                                                                           
